latestPosts.caption:
| The Shashthi Edit

Well BoroMashi @soma_gupta was clear on this one - “it’s not only for jamais in our home” she said & continues “it is for our children too, to celebrate them !! - something I learnt from my mother in law”. 

Clearly her MIL - our loving Chhanda Didu was way ahead of her time. 

So taking this tradition forward Mashi cooked a plethora of food, with special focus on fish which included ilish Mesho’s @badsha.gupta.92 favourite & the most delectable Boal being mine.

The Ambol was to die for - light & the perfect sweet, tart & a speck savoury. The mutton chops were just done right - with the most simple ingredients & flavour complexity pro max !! 

@snez_95 @riks_dev missed you guys - let’s plan the next one together ❣️

Mashi thank you for making this so special - our tummies & hearts are so full. Muchos Gracias. Love You. ❤️
